social_posts.post_text:
Sometimes it takes making a reel to realize how amazing a year has been! Thank you 2022 for being good to me, even though at times it felt like I was just moving through the months and checking things off the list. Now looking back, I can say it was a year full of milestones & beautiful moments:
- moving from Sicily to San Diego and changing our lives completely again
- organizing a conference for 1500+ people in Switzerland
- renovating not 1 but 2 apartments in Sicily (with none of the workers speaking english) 
- improving my Italian
- spending more time with family & friends 
- learning how to sail
…and much more

Thank you 2022 and cheers to a New Year 🥂🍾

The feeling is hard to describe when you arrive at White Pocket. The beautiful swirling, soft, glowing white rock face dotted with pools of water mirroring back the sky.

Getting here is by no means easy, it’s a 2.5hr drive from the nearest town and don’t try to attempt it without a 4x4 high clearance car. We got stuck in the sand and almost didn’t make it before the sun set. We spent a couple hours digging the car out but it was definitely worth the 30 minutes of magic at the end. 

#whitepocket #vermillioncliffs #vermillioncliffsnationalmonument #arizona #whitepocketarizona #roadtripusa

Kaua’i | Paradise 🌈

One of the truly breathtaking places on Earth. 

Named “The Garden Island” of Hawaii, Kauai is covered in tropical rainforests, emerald valleys, spectacular mountain spires, jagged cliffs and the most stunning waterfalls. 

I had this island on my bucket list for 10 years and it was just as incredible as I imaged it would be. Seeing it from above, in its full majesty was the 🍒 on top! If you ever want to do a doors-off helicopter tour, this is the place to do it!
